  <div class="row my-5 bg-light p-5 rounded text-center shadow">
    <h3 class="fw-bold">Join Us Today!</h3>
    <p class="text-muted">Start managing your mess or employees more effectively with our user-friendly platform.</p>
    <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
